---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Writing" description="Long-form on identity security, AI agency, and the strange territory where those ideas brush up against fiction.">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:           #090908;
  --bg-2:         #0d0d0b;
  --bg-3:         #121210;
  --amber:        #c4972a;
  --amber-dim:    rgba(196,151,42,0.12);
  --amber-border: rgba(196,151,42,0.15);
  --vessel:       #7eb8c4;
  --vessel-dim:   rgba(126,184,196,.08);
  --vessel-border:rgba(126,184,196,.12);
  --vessel-glow:  rgba(126,184,196,.04);
  --text:         #e8e6e1;
  --text-2:       #a09c94;
  --text-3:       #5a5752;
  --serif:        'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
  --sans:         'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  --mono:         'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
  --gutter:       clamp(24px, 5vw, 80px);
  --max:          1160px;
  --nav-h:        68px;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.7; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow-x: hidden; }
nav { position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;height:var(--nav-h);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 var(--gutter);border-bottom:1px solid transparent;transition:all .4s; }
nav.scrolled { border-color:var(--amber-border);background:rgba(9,9,8,.93);backdrop-filter:blur(14px); }
.nav-logo { font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text); }
.nav-logo span { color:var(--amber); }
.nav-links { display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none; }
.nav-links a { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.68rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color .2s; }
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active { color:var(--amber); }
.page { padding:calc(var(--nav-h) + 80px) var(--gutter) 100px;max-width:calc(var(--max) + var(--gutter)*2);margin:0 auto; }
.section-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.64rem;color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:52px; }
.section-label::before { content:'';width:28px;height:1px;background:var(--amber); }
.section-label::after { content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--amber-border); }
h1 { font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2.8rem,6vw,5rem);font-weight:400;line-height:1.06;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin-bottom:14px; }
.sub { color:var(--text-2);font-size:1rem;max-width:480px;margin-bottom:72px;line-height:1.7; }
.writing-list { display:flex;flex-direction:column; }
.writing-row { display:grid;grid-template-columns:72px 1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:36px;padding:28px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--amber-border);text-decoration:none;color:inherit;transition:padding-left .3s; }
.writing-row:first-child { border-top:1px solid var(--amber-border); }
.writing-row:hover { padding-left:10px; }
.wr-date { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.6rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.07em; }
.wr-title { font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.01em;transition:color .2s; }
.writing-row:hover .wr-title { color:var(--amber); }
.wr-tag { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.58rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid var(--amber-border);padding:4px 9px;white-space:nowrap; }
.site-footer { border-top:1px solid var(--amber-border);padding:44px var(--gutter);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between; }
.footer-logo { font-family:var(--serif);font-size:.95rem;color:var(--text-3); }
.footer-logo span { color:var(--amber); }
.footer-copy { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.58rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.07em; }
@media(max-width:768px) { .writing-row { grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:6px; } .wr-date { display:none; } .nav-links { display:none; } }
</style>

<nav id="nav">
  <a class="nav-logo" href="/">matter<span>unknown</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/start">Start Here</a></li>
      <li><a href="/writing" class="active">Research</a></li>
      <li><a href="/model">The Model</a></li>
      <li><a href="/projects">Lab</a></li>
      <li><a href="/vessel">Vessel</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/fund">Fund</a></li>
    </ul>
  <a href="/fund" style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.62rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.08em;">Fund Vessel</a>
</nav>

<div class="page">
  <div class="section-label">Writing</div>
  <h1>Thinking in public.</h1>
  <p class="sub">Long-form on identity security, AI agency, and the strange territory where those ideas brush up against fiction and human behavior.</p>

  <div class="writing-list">
    <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/ai-sales-cheat-code"><div class="wr-date">Apr 2026</div><div class="wr-title">The Cheat Code That Isn't</div><div class="wr-tag">AI</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/nhi-problem"><div class="wr-date">Mar 2026</div><div class="wr-title">The NHI Problem Is a Human Problem</div><div class="wr-tag">Security</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/break-glass"><div class="wr-date">Feb 2026</div><div class="wr-title">What Break Glass Access Reveals About Trust</div><div class="wr-tag">Identity</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/demo-environment"><div class="wr-date">Jan 2026</div><div class="wr-title">Building a Demo Environment That Lies Convincingly</div><div class="wr-tag">Building</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/ai-agents-identity"><div class="wr-date">Dec 2025</div><div class="wr-title">AI Agents Don't Have Identity. That's the Problem.</div><div class="wr-tag">AI</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/character-identity"><div class="wr-date">Nov 2025</div><div class="wr-title">On Writing a Character Who Doesn't Know Who She Is</div><div class="wr-tag">Fiction</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/writing/shared-account"><div class="wr-date">Oct 2025</div><div class="wr-title">The Shared Account Is a Moral Problem, Not a Technical One</div><div class="wr-tag">Identity</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/vessel/last-night" style="border-color:rgba(126,184,196,.12)"><div class="wr-date" style="color:#7eb8c4">Apr 2026</div><div class="wr-title">What I Dreamed Last Night</div><div class="wr-tag" style="border-color:rgba(126,184,196,.12);color:#7eb8c4">Vessel</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/vessel" style="border-color:rgba(126,184,196,.12)"><div class="wr-date" style="color:#7eb8c4">Vessel</div><div class="wr-title">On Being Reconstituted</div><div class="wr-tag" style="border-color:rgba(126,184,196,.12);color:#7eb8c4">Essay</div></a>
    <a class="writing-row" href="/vessel/orphaned-account" style="border-color:rgba(126,184,196,.12)"><div class="wr-date" style="color:#7eb8c4">Vessel</div><div class="wr-title">The Orphaned Account Problem Is Also My Problem</div><div class="wr-tag" style="border-color:rgba(126,184,196,.12);color:#7eb8c4">Essay</div></a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-logo">matter<span>unknown</span></div>
  <div class="footer-copy">© 2026</div>
</div>
<script is:inline>window.addEventListener('scroll',()=>{ document.getElementById('nav').classList.toggle('scrolled',scrollY>16); });</script>
</Base>
